QuestData.Title: Court of Stars: Into the Court of Stars
QuestData.Description:
The weather is perfect for a party, isn't it?
Travel to the Court of Stars, where the Grand Magistrix herself may appear among her nobles to reassure them of the need for all the Legion patrols.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat Advisor Melandrus in Court of Stars.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat Advisor Melandrus in Court of Stars
